movie star who is one of India's most politically powerful and
dependably outlandish figures, faces charges that she thrashed her
former accountant with high-heeled shoes, beating him
black-and-blue during an hourlong ordeal that left him bed-ridden
with a bandaged right eye. By Barry Bearak.
</P>
