<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    SUVs: How big is too big?
 &HT;    By Matt Reed
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Just what we need: one more guilt-trip
about living in the 'burbs.
</P>
<P>
   Bad enough already that our sport-utility vehicles burn gas by
