<P>
   IRELAND-CARBOMB (Belfast) _ For many civil rights lawyers in
Ireland, Monday's bomb assassination of their colleague, Rosemary
Nelson, was a terrifying reminder of past horrors. Many are
worrying they might be next. By Kevin Cullen. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   IRELAND-POLITICS (Washington) _ Many of the key political
players in the Irish peace process plan meetings with Sen. Kennedy,
President Clinton, others. By Anne E. Kornblut. 650 words.
</P>
<P>
